text.paragraph:
Avoid abrupt withdrawal from levetiracetam injection in order to reduce the risk of increased seizure frequency and status epilepticus [see 

                              Warnings and Precautions (5.7)

                           ].

Levetiracetam blood levels may decrease during pregnancy [see 

                                    Warnings and Precautions (5.10)

                                 ].

Levetiracetam levels may decrease during pregnancy [see
Warnings and Precautions (5.10
) and Use in Specific Populations (8.1)].
